With only a little over a teaspoon for the curry paste, why bother?! At least 2 ounces of curry paste should be used (and up to 4 oz). No wonder everyone said it was so bland. Also consider that commercial curry pastes vary greatly in degree of spiciness and depth of taste. Mae Ploy from Thailand is a good ready made paste and also Nittaya brand.

